These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
City: colone, new-york, boston, hannover
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, classical, punk, rock
4 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, turtle, guinea-pig
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, aconite, rose
 1. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 2. the person who growsmarigold is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
 3. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 5. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person who growsmarigold##8
 6. the fan of punk is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
 8. the fan of rock is between the person who growsdahlia and the owner of the mouse##2
 9. the person who growsrose is the fan of punk##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
12. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
13. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
14. the person traveling to new-york is the person who growsaconite##1
15. the person traveling to new-york is not the owner of the mouse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City         | colone     | new-york   | hannover | boston |
| Music-Genre   | classical | rock   | disco   | punk  |
| Pet         | mouse  | turtle  | guinea-pig  | hamster |
| Flower     | marigold    | aconite | dahlia     | rose    |

