 1. the person who growsaconite is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who growsbellflower##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the cain-smoker##8
 5. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 7. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
 8. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
11. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
12. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
14. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
15. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
17. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who growsbellflower##8
18. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
