.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, may, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, teacher, manager, paramedic
City: hamburg, paris, nizza, hannover
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, chestnut, coral, grey
 1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 5. the person who likes coral is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the manager##8
 7. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
 8. the manager is on the left of the paramedic##1
 9. the paramedic is on the left of the teacher##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
11. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
12. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | november    | january   | may | december |
| Job   | entrepreneur     | manager  | paramedic   | teacher      |
| City   | paris | hamburg    | nizza      | hannover       |
| Color         | coral    | red | grey   | chestnut    |

