10. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growsbegonia##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the colonial house##8
12. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
13. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
14. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
