 4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the palace house##2
 6. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
 7. the person eating potato is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person eating grapes##6
